--- OVERVIEW: Mg2P2O7 ---

This folder collects all calculations concerning the Mg2P2O7 (bimagnesium pyrophosphate)
system: classical/AIMD dynamics, DeePMD-driven steered and OPES MD, and ORCA benchmark
quantum-chemistry calculations used to build reference configurations.

o pyro-hydrolysis-mg.pdb: top-level reference geometry of the hydrolysis system (PDB format).

o pyro-hydrolysis-mg2.mol2: top-level reference geometry with bond/connectivity info (MOL2 format).

--- SUBFOLDERS ---

o CP2K_dynamics/: CP2K ab initio MD of the PPiMg2 system.
  - inputs/: base CP2K input files (PPiMg2.inp, PPiMg2_edges.inp) for the two initial
    coordination geometries explored (bridged vs. edge-sharing Mg binding).
  - PPiMg2_sides_final/: final production CP2K inputs (three protocol variants: original,
    2nd, and side-chain corrected), the resulting energy series (PPiMg2_sides-Energy.en),
    energy-distribution plots (energy_distribution_Kcal.png, energy_distribution_PPiMg2_sides.png),
    the energy-extraction scripts used to produce them (energy_grep*.py), the SLURM submission
    script (job_slurm_submission_cp2k.sh), and a VMD visualization script (vmd-pyrophosphate.tcl).

o LAMMPS_MD_PPiMg2/: steered MD of Mg2P2O7 driven by PLUMED using the DeePMD NNP committee
  from ArcaNN iteration 006. See its own README (cluster session log) for a detailed,
  dated history of this run, including a PLUMED wall miscalibration bug and its fix.

o SMD/: LAMMPS topology/trajectory and PLUMED setup (plumed_Mg_complex.dat) for an earlier,
  Mg-constrained steered-MD run of the sides configuration (properties_sys1-2.dat holds
  associated atom-type/property definitions).

o hydrolysis_OPES/: OPES (On-the-fly Probability Enhanced Sampling)-driven hydrolysis MD of
  the Mg complex using the NNP, with its LAMMPS input/topology (ppimg2-hydrolysis.in/.lmp),
  PLUMED OPES setup (plumed_ppimg2-hydrolysis.dat), the raw PLUMED output (opes_MD.dat), the
  SLURM submission script, and a VMD visualization script.

o orca/: ORCA benchmark single-point/optimization calculations for candidate Mg-pyrophosphate
  coordination geometries.
  - PPi2Mg_2b_bridged/: bidentate-bridged Mg coordination.
  - PPi2Mg_2b_up_down/: bidentate up-down Mg coordination, including a solvated ("nowater"
    stripped) variant with full ORCA output (densities, Hessian, gradient, property files)
    and a solvation/ subfolder with the packmol-built explicit-water system and its LAMMPS
    topology conversions.
  - PPi2Mg_3b/: tridentate Mg coordination.
  - configurations/: reference structures (.xyz/.pdb) for each coordination mode, used as
    starting points for the ORCA calculations above.

Note: this README was written to give a general overview of pre-existing content; no
existing file in this tree was modified to produce it.
